smell of an oily rag
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:usu. in the phrase to live on (or off) the smell of an oily rag: to live frugally, on very little (esp. as regards food)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
